1. Core Concept (Non-Negotiable)

This app is a School Management System (SMS) like Eskooly, NOT:

a teacher app

a student app

an attendance app

Everything hangs on School ‚Üí People ‚Üí Academic Structure ‚Üí Operations.



üí° Key rule:
Teacher is NOT special in code. It‚Äôs just an employee with teaching permissions.

